<br>
How soon should you start? As soon as you can. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->    Though it really depends on which server you're on. If you're on FV, don't wait too long or you'll fall victim to the TLC. <br>
<br>
Personally, I waited until level 29 to start mine, got the torch right away, and the other 3 over the following 2 weeks (I couldn't stand camping there for too long, so I spent time xping to break up the monotony.)<br>
<br>
I was able to solo many of the mages in Najena at 29, only the basement spawns gave me trouble due to adds. If you can put a group together, you should be able to pull it off easily at your current level. <p>Naladini <BR>
Elementalist of the 53rd Season-Stormhammer<BR>
