<br>
At your Level you will be able to solo the top floor mages (3) and the guards and Tentacle Terrors.<br>
If you time it right, you are able to solo the whole top floor and be full mana when they repop (If I remember correctly Najena is on a 20 minute timer - so you have some time to med inbetween).<br>
<br>
The &quot;hard part&quot; (not that hard, but a bit difficult) is to break the 2 mages in the Crystal Room. To try that you better be full mana.<br>
<br>
Once broken, the top floor will be very nice for cash and exp - and while you level there you get the 4 items for the foci and maybe even the 4 pages of elemental mastery (epic quest).<br>
<br>
I found it very worth the time, cause I got my foci and made some nice levels there as well.<br>
<br>
Just start slowly to check how much you can do - then extend the area you hunt in.<br>
<br>
In the end I killed the 4 mages, the 4 tentacles and all the elementals on that floor without any trouble.<br>
<br>
Cheers,<br>
<br>
